<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567764' id='t-567764'>That really is strange. How do we explain this?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570253' id='t-570253'>Well, to do that, one thing is we can look at the deception-detection literature.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573632' id='t-573632'>It's a very old literature by now, it's coming up on 50 years.</span>
