<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608612' id='t-608612'>Most of you would say that one of the cues you look at</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611042' id='t-611042'>is the eyes. The eyes are the window to the soul.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613770' id='t-613770'>And you're not alone. Around the world, almost every culture,</span>
