<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619036' id='t-619036'>over the last 50 years says there's actually no reliable cue</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622860' id='t-622860'>to deception, which blew me away, and it's one of</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625857' id='t-625857'>the hard lessons that I learned when I was customs officer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628212' id='t-628212'>The eyes do not tell us whether somebody's lying or not.</span>
